Enum FileUpload

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<FileUpload>
bss.Data.FileUpload
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<FileUpload>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum FileUpload extends Enum<FileUpload>
Enum for handling different types of file uploads and processing.

This enum provides different implementations for reading files based on their type and structure.
